- make an empty activity.

- first thing we put a dependency in the gradle file , and classpath and apply plugin.

- make a activity --> type fragment and viewModel.

- now we can create  navigation_graph.xml --> click on res and choose Navigation .

- on the main activity choose container and choose nav_host_fragment

- host will show in navigation_graph

- click on new destination button and choose main fragment as the destination

- now you can use navigation graph to add new fragment

- now in main activity we should implement interface OnFragmentInteractionListener

- now make arrow with the main fragment and the second fragment --> should make build and generated java ....

- now you can run the code

- how to send args from one fragment to another fragment
    - in the navigation graph we will make an args in the second fragment -- > name

    - send the args from first activity to the second activity
